Use launch for deploying node projects
https://github.com/bengourley/launch



SETUP A NEW NODE SERVER
=======================

1) add your key to ~/.ssh/authorized_keys on the server

2) rsync setupserver washplant-live.conf <user>@<host>:/home/<user/

3) ssh into server and run ./setupserver

4) Customize upstart configuration <app>-live.conf and put in /etc/init:
    - use app-data for username unless changed in setupserver script
